review_title: Couldn't set code, immediately got stuck, poor quality
reviews: DO NOT BUY, not good quality
They did not last long and were not strong or durable. I do not recommend.

review_title: They are screws and they work as expected
Crooked at bottom. Doesn't seem very springy when pushing it up.
reviews: Overall, these blinds are not quite satisfactory because when they are pulled down they are not straight and when I push them up it feels like they don't really want to go up. They were easy to install though and the appearance is fine otherwise. Also, the first set of blinds that I received were defective, but the seller replaced them for me.

review_title: Okay pants, shirt fit not so comfortable but good price
reviews:
Overall, these underwear were a bit thick, but not actually so warm considering their thickness. I might possibly buy a set again since they are so affordable, but I do not love them. The shirt's cut did not feel comfortable the first time I put it on.

The pants do the job though as a second layer over my other better pair of thermal underpants. They are not bad - they are okay.

The material is thin but keeps me warm. In 0 degree Celsius I wear these under my jeans and I am warm to walk to work (20 minute walk). I wouldn't want to have to stand outside a long time with just these under my jeans in below freezing weather, but they are good if you will be active. I like that they are thin and that they never feel sweaty or moist. In 17 degree below 0 weather I need another layer over them or I would be too cold. I am 5'9" and 150 lbs (69 kg) and the size medium fits great.
I like the design and appearance of these. It was easy to install. I would definitely buy again.

review_title: Not so heavy and maybe not greatest for thermal
reviews: Overall, these curtains look okay. They are not so heavy and I don't think they have that much insulating effect. I might look for a different curtain if I had to buy again. The pink color looks good though.
These are great. They are easy to use. However, I agree with another reviewer that the manufacturer is using too much packaging and it doesn't need a user manual.

Overall, this hat is warm. If it is -5 degrees Celcius or higher I don't wear my hood. If it is much colder than -5 degrees Celsius then the hat is not enough and I put my jacket's hood on. I think this hat will be fine all winter. I have not had any quality issues with it so far.
These are excellent bags. I like them but I might buy paper bags next time because my cities waste management department prefers we use paper bags.
Overall, it is doing its job. I have not had any problems with it although I have only had it for three months.

review_title: Good product, probably could find something more affordable locally
reviews: Overall the scarf is warm and comfortable, but I think I can find something similar at dollar store for a fraction of the price.

review_title: Excellent, battery is lasting a very long time
reviews: Overall, this product is just as I expected. I did not have any surprises. It is good.

I ended up buying a pair of gloves at a local store which I am wearing all the time. I probably shouldn't have purchased these because...
- they are not waterproof
- I think like most knit mittens, they will stretch around my wrists and not keep out the snow
- they are a little difficult to put on or take off.

All of the cons to these mittens are more a con to buying knit mittens. Overall, these were well-made, but I think I would not buy again because I prefer a thick waterproof glove instead.
